  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "SEC1",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Location Master Data in SAP TM"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Location is one of the most critical master data objects in SAP TM. Every transportation process starts from a source location and ends at a destination location. Locations represent physical places where transportation activities occur."
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC3",
      "type": "callout",
      "calloutType": "important",
      "title": "Key Concept",
      "content": "Without valid Locations, SAP TM cannot create Freight Units, determine routes, calculate distances or perform transportation planning."
    },
    {
