    {
      "id": "SEC12",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Business Scenario"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC13",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "ABC Manufacturing ships products from its Hyderabad Plant to customers in Bengaluru. SAP TM identifies the pickup Location (Plant), delivery Location (Customer), validates the Transportation Lane and plans the shipment using the available Resources."
    },
    {
